two laptop computers containing investigation materials about the cause of princess diana 's death were stolen
afp , london , 6th .
london daily express pointed out that two laptop computers , which contain investigation materials about the car accident and death of princess diana in 1997 , were stolen from the office of the former metropolitan police chief .
the report pointed out that this larceny case has brought people 's speculation that those computers might conceal confidential materials from the investigation led by stevens , the former metropolitan police chief .
however , a spokeswoman for the metropolitan police bureau said that there is no sensitive information or any materials related to the investigation on those computers .
sir stevens is the head of the northumbria police bureau in the uk. his office is located in the newcastle area on the thames river .
the report pointed out that police officers from the northumbria police bureau have been investigating two larceny cases in the past ten days .
one of the cases occurred during the weekend break from january 28 to 29 , and computers and cash were taken . the second larceny case took place last week , and there were no losses involved .
the northumbria police bureau also stated that there is no evidence showing that the two larceny cases are related to the work of sir stevens .
stevens has been investigating whether the cause of the death of diana , princess of wales , was not directly from the car accident .
burgess , a royal coroner , issued an ordinance in 2004 to continue searching for related evidence .
princess diana lost her life in a car accident in a paris tunnel on august 31 , 1997 ; her lover fayed and the driver also died with her .
after a two - year investigation , the french police think that the tragedy was caused by the driver , who was drunk and took drugs , drove the car too fast , and lost control of the car .
the two belligerent parties in sri lanka agreed to hold negotiations in geneva late this month
afp , colombo , 7th .
norway , as a mediator for the peace process , said that belligerent groups in sri lanka agreed to hold negotiations in geneva , switzerland , on the 22nd of this month , finally breaking the stalemate on negotiations - which has stagnated for three years - to end the several dozen years of bloody ethnic conflicts pursued by the parties .
this breakthrough was achieved after solheim , a norwegian envoy for peace , met with balasingham , a negotiation representative for the liberation tigers of tamil eelam , in london .
the norwegian embassy here said in a statement that " the belligerent parties in sri lanka , that is the government of sri lanka and the liberation tigers of tamil eelam , have requested the norwegian government to assist in holding two - day negotiations from february 22 to 23 in geneva . "
the two - day negotiations will focus on how to strengthen the cease - fire agreement effected on february 23,2002 ; this agreement has not been fully complied with by both sides .
the norwegian embassy pointed out that , " both sides will discuss how to improve the implementation of the cease - fire agreement , which is the first time for both sides to have face - to - face negotiations at such a high level . "
solheim said that he will lead a norwegian delegation participating in the negotiations ; balasingham will lead the four delegates of the liberation tigers of tamil eelam , and the health minister will be the head of the government ( delegation ) of sri lanka .
he said , " this is a small step but an important one on the road of peace , and it is expected to be difficult for the negotiation process . "
the previous face - to - face negotiations for resolving the ethnic conflicts in sri lanka were held in march , 2003 , in japan , but the liberation tigers of tamil eelam cancelled the seventh round of negotiations originally scheduled for thailand in april , 2003 .
turin winter olympic games unveiled , and both north and south korean delegations marched into the stadium together while holding hands
afp , turin , italy , 10th .
the 20th winter olympic games held their opening ceremony today in turin , and the delegations from north and south korea , who were enemies during the cold war , marched into the stadium together while holding hands during the entrance ceremony .
lee bo - ra , a south korean women 's speed skating athlete , and han jong - in , a north korean men 's figure skating athlete , were the flag bearers , respectively , for the delegations of the two countries , and led both north and south korean delegations marching into the winter olympic games stadium .
this is the first time for the olympic delegations of both north and south korea to march together into the winter olympic games stadium while holding hands .
to reflect the spirit of friendship , reconciliation , and unity of both sides in recent years , the delegations from north and south korea marched into the stadium when the 2000 summer olympic games in sydney and the 2004 summer olympic games in athens were held .
north korea did not participate in the 19th winter olympic games held in salt lake city , in the united states .
the korean peninsula was divided into capitalist south korea and communist north korea in 1948 , and both sides were enemies during the korean war from 1950 to 1953 .
the relations between the two sides were improved after the summit meeting for peace held between leaders of north and south korea in 2000 .
according to tradition , the first nation marching into the stadium was the greek delegation , south korea was the 22nd one , and north korea was the 23rd one among the 80 countries to participate in the games .
the last nation marching into the stadium was the italian delegation as the host country . when it entered the stadium , warm welcoming applause immediately rose throughout the stadium .
hoffman used to be addicted to drugs and fortunately woke up in time and created his performance career
afp , new york , 16th .
philip seymour hoffman , the lead actor in the movie capote : a cold - blooded confession , who is publicly acknowledged as the one with the most hope of winning oscar 's best actor award this year , disclosed that he used to be addicted to drugs and liquor and could not give them up when he was young and reckless , but fortunately he was able to give them up successfully , and create his performance career and reach the peak .
when he was interviewed by the united states ' cbs news magazine 60 minutes , he softly sighed that he really tried to obtain drugs and liquor by hook or by crook during that period .
he was little more than 20 years old then , and just graduated from the drama department of new york university . entered into the multi - colored society with its quick - spinning pace of life , he got dizzy with the whirlwind life and lost control of himself .
he enrolled in a substance abuse treatment clinic at age 22 and gave up his addictive habit of alcohol and drugs there , which was the most panic - inducing period in his life .
hoffman is thought of as the actor with the most hope of winning the best actor award at the upcoming oscar awards ceremony next month because of his performance in the movie capote : a cold - blooded confession , interpreting the american author capote .
his great performance skills have been acknowledged long before this , and won the acknowledgements of many awards , including the best actor golden globe award .
the thirty - eight - year - old actor stated in the interview that it would have been impossible for him to be nominated for the oscar award if he had not made the painful decision to change his bad habits before he became famous .
he said that he really admires those beautiful nineteen - year - old actresses who suddenly become famous and rich .
signs of bird flu emerge everywhere in europe , and people are in a panic in nigeria
afp , brussels , 16th .
signs of bird flu virus continue to emerge in europe and send people into panic .
the executive committee of the european union has passed a resolution for the establishment of additional " buffer area " controls , including all areas of countries where the virus has been discovered for control , and forbidding all trade and transportation of poultries and bird species .
the bird flu breakouts continue to spread to more chicken farms following the eighth day since the deadly h 5n1 virus was discovered in nigeria , africa , and tracks demonstrate that it has crossed the northern border of nigeria and entered into niger .
egyptian officials are investigating the sudden mass death of chickens on a chicken farm in the south , and there is concern that the virus might continue to spread .
chicken meat markets in europe are falling to a great extent because of the impact of the virus event . the executive committee of the european union stressed that there is no reason to panic .
jipu ruinuo , an executive member of the committee responsible for sanitation and food safety , said that it is understandable for people to be concerned about the event but there is no need for overreaction .
the executive committee of the european union has issued a new regulation and listed all of the european areas where the virus has been discovered as " buffer areas " after passing a previous resolution about the establishment of a three - kilometer protection area and ten - kilometer warning area around every virus discovery spot .
an official for the european union , who preferred to remain anonymous , pointed out that everyone is very nervous , and processing news from everywhere in europe about suspicions of breakouts of the epidemic .
until now , the h 5n1 virus has been discovered in european regions including austria , bulgaria , croatia , germany , greece , italy , romania , slovenia , ukraine , and russia , and has been discovered almost exclusively in groups of wild swans .
on the 16th , romania discovered its 31st epidemic case , and slovenia , austria , greece , and ruegen island in germany have also discovered new epidemic cases .
the bird flu virus was discovered in the bodies of two ducks in southern italy , which are the first poultry infected with the h 5n1 virus in the european region , aside from wild swans .
the greatest concern that european union officials have is those migrant birds that will be flying back from africa .
the nigerian government is strengthening its work to prevent the human infection of the virus on the african continent .
the nigerian government announced that all poultries and bird species must be destroyed within a five - kilometer area of where an infected farm is discovered , regardless of whether they are threatened by the virus or not .
the government of niger , its neighbor country , has announced a national warning state , and made an emergency plan by providing 4 million usd to monitor the border areas with nigeria .
the newly established national emergency committee stated that they have received a report that nearly 400 poultries and bird species are dead in magaria , a loosely guarded area between the two countries .
china 's new electronic banking business management regulations will be implemented on march 1
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 6 ( reporter : han jie and xu bo ) reporters learned from china 's banking supervision committee on the 6th that the " electronic banking business management method " and the " guidance on electronic banks security assessment " issued by the banking supervision committee in recent days will be implemented on march 1 , 2006 .
a spokesman for the banking supervision committee said that based on the management method regulations , the approval method for foreign financial institutions is unchanged , i.e. if a branch of a foreign bank is approved to establish an online banking business and it needs to add a new service item for the online banking business , the major unit that reports to the branch in china 's territory should be solely responsible for the application and review .
to normalize banking business development of commercial banks that use the internet , the chinese people 's bank has made and issued the " temporary method for management of online banking businesses " in june , 2001 .
the spokesman for the banking supervision committee said that with the continuous development of electronic banking business at commercial banks , the temporary method cannot meet the requirements for electronic banking risk control anymore . thus , the banking supervision committee has made two new regulations .
as the spokesman for the banking supervision committee introduced , the acknowledgement of the banking supervision committee on qualification of a security assessment setup is different from industrial admission or administrative approval for admission qualification for enterprises , and it is not a necessary condition for an assessment setup to conduct its security assessment business for electronic banking , and it is only a reference when financial institutions select an assessment setup .
as long as a security assessment setup follows related conditions and requirements , even if it is not acknowledged by the banking supervision committee for its qualification , financial institutions can still invite it to conduct an assessment for electronic banking security , but it should be controlled according to related regulations .
the " method for management of electronic banking businesses " has a total of nine chapters and 99 articles that are divided into nine parts , including the general principle , application and renewal , risk control , data exchange and transfer control , business contract control , cross - border business activities control , supervision control , liabilities , and additional regulations , etc.
the " guidance on electronic banks security assessment " has a total of five chapters and 57 articles that are divided into five parts , including the general principle , security assessment setup , implementation of security assessment , management of security assessment activities , and additional regulations , etc.
publication of on investigations and studies by mao zedong , zhou enlai , liu shaoqi , zhu de , deng xiaoping , and chen yun
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 6. the book on investigations and studies by mao zedong , zhou enlai , liu shaoqi , zhu de , deng xiaoping , and chen yun , compiled by the document studies office of the central committee of the chinese communist party , has been published in recent days by the document studies office of the central committee .
