the old generation of revolutionaries , including mao zedong , zhou enlai , liu shaoqi , zhu de , deng xiaoping , and chen yun , used to publish many important and brilliant discussion documents on the issues of investigations and studies . they also often went to grass - root units , conducted social investigations themselves , and wrote many investigative reports .
the practices and accomplishments of their investigations and studies have played important roles in guiding developments of the party 's and people 's cause along a correct path .
the book on investigations and studies by mao zedong , zhou enlai , liu shaoqi , zhu de , deng xiaoping , and chen yun is divided into three parts : the first part includes selected and compiled comments and words of the old generation of revolutionaries , including mao zedong , on investigations and studies ; the second part contains selected articles by mao zedong and the old generation of revolutionaries on investigations and studies ; the third part involves those investigative reports written by the three investigation groups sent by mao zedong , and also written by liu shaoqi , zhou enlai , zhu de , chen yun , and deng xiaoping in the beginning of the 60s of the last century .
