since 2006 , 4 chinese citizens have been killed , one after another , in south africa , and the chinese world has broadly paid attention to it .
china 's foreign ministry has contacted the south african side about the matter , and warned chinese citizens who are traveling in south africa to increase their awareness of their security and protection , and to strengthen unity and caring for each other among overseas chinese , and to collaborate with the police to jointly strike against criminal activities .
" we express our sincerest sympathy and condolences to family members of those victims . "
vusi bruce koloane said , " we are sorry for this , and we also want the chinese people to believe that the south african government is carefully investigating every case related to the chinese . "
as the embassy of south africa presented , the south african police have successfully broken a case in which chen jianqing , a woman came from fujian , china , was killed on february 5 in south africa , and have arrested a suspect .
the police are searching for another suspect at present .
as the south african embassy in china disclosed , the suspect , who is charged with the gun death of a hong kong businessman in january of this year , has been arrested by the south african police , and the belongings of the victim have been recovered .
when talking about the possible impacts of the killings of chinese citizens , vusi bruce koloane thinks that those incidents will " indeed " impact trade , tourism , and exchanges in other fields between the two countries , and produce negative outcomes . but in the long run , those impacts " should not be big . "
as tourist attache of the south african embassy nian beixi presented , the embassy issued more than 2,000 visas for chinese to go to south africa in the first 15 days of this year .
based on the statistical data of the chinese government , south africa had maintained its number one status as china 's biggest trade partner in africa in 2005 .
the bilateral trade amount reached 7.27 billion usd , and increased 23 % compared with that of last year .
however , people in the tourist industry think that the continuous occurrences of killing chinese citizens in 2004 have apparently affected the number of tourists who visited south africa .
based on the statistics of the sightseeing bureau of south africa , there were 20,331 chinese tourists who visited south africa in the first half of 2005 , which were reduced 14.9 % compared with that of last year .
there are about 200,000 chinese who live in south africa at present , and are scattered everywhere in the towns and villages of south africa .
analysts here think that since there are big gaps between the rich and poor in south african society , and a high unemployment rate , guns are spread everywhere , and no death penalty , the crime rate is still high there .
because many chinese do not speak english , and they carry cash with them and put cash in their homes , they become easy targets for criminals to attack them for their assets .
( hong kong , macao , and taiwan ) hong kong promotes occupational english study and training
xinhua news agency , hong kong , february 13. the " occupational english campaign " launched by the government of hong kong special administrative region made a new plan on the 13th to make more on - the - job people upgrade their english level .
the plan , named " studying english well for enrichment of life , " includes a series of publicity activities to promote occupational english study and training , and let employers further learn how to help their employees upgrade their english level .
as of now , the plan has funded 25,000 people to complete english training courses , and meet hong kong 's occupational english requirements related to their job categories .
the hong kong " occupational english campaign " was launched by the government of the special administrative region in 2000 .
one important project of the " occupational english campaign " is to provide an assistance plan for occupational english training .
the plan refers to helping employees who need to use english in their work through participating in training and taking designated international business english tests to reach the occupational english level required in their job categories .
aids test will be free , voluntary , and confidential in hebei
xinhua news agency , shi jiazhang , february 14 ( reporter : dong zhiyong ) . the health bureau of hebei province issued the work solution for voluntary consulting aids test in hebei province ( trial ) a few days ago , and clearly stipulated that the aids test follows free , voluntary , and confidential principles , and hopes to identify aids infectors and patients to the maximum , and to further implement prevention and intervention measures , and the " four free - one care " policy .
the solution confirms the working principle for voluntary consulting aids testing in hebei province : aids antibody tests and consultations are free ; aids antibody tests and consultations are voluntary and of informed consent ; aids antibody tests and consultations are confidential , and there is no assessment of consulters ' related behavior ; the legal rights and interest of aids virus infectors and patients are protected , and subsequent appropriate services are provided for them .
the solution requires that aids consultation test sites should be established at convenient places for consulters , and separate rooms should be used for one - on - one consulting in order to protect the consulters ' privacy .
selection of consultants should fully consider individuals ' quality , sense of responsibility , knowledge and communication ability , etc.
to protect the privacy of consulters , test forms can be registered with codes or serial numbers .
the solution also requires that health administrative units at the county level or above should publish the names and consultation phone numbers of local medical and health institutions responsible for voluntary and free aids tests in the major local media , and make it convenient for the masses to know related information .
working priority of public security ministry still focused on supervision and investigation on forcing confessions by torture
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 14 ( reporter : meng na ) . deputy director of the police affairs supervision and investigation bureau of the public security ministry zheng baigang pointed out when answering foreign reporters ' questions in a news conference held by the public security bureau on the 14th , that the so - called " using of methods that are not totally proper to make a crime suspect make a confession " are never allowed in china .
the working priority of the supervision and investigation departments is also to prevent these problems from happening .
he also pointed out that some international organizations do not have a thorough and correct understanding of the law enforcement status of china 's police .
the newest material provided by the public security ministry on the 14th demonstrates that the case records regulation on implementation of detention by public security organizations and regulation on continuous interrogation used by public security organizations issued by the public security ministry in 2002 and 2004 , respectively , have better assured local public security units of using detention and interrogation measures according to the law .
since 1997 , to further promote the " three corrections " ( i.e. corrections of forcing confessions by torture , abuse of guns and equipment by the police , and abuse of coercive measures ) , the public security 's police affairs supervision and investigation forces have gone into grass - roots and front law enforcement units including street police stations , police teams , police patrol teams , police traffic teams , and supervision and control sites of public security units , to enforce laws on site . they have investigated law enforcement links publicly that involve citizens ' personal security and rights , and made private visits for them in order to look for oversights and errors by law enforcement units , and to remind and warn them to avoid mistakes from the beginning .
to prevent the occurrence of law enforcement problems from the beginning , police affairs supervision and investigation units have further stretched their law enforcement supervision and investigation antennas , and strengthened the supervision and investigation on law enforcement links including use of subpoena measures , inquiry and interrogation , 110 contact with the police , registered case statistics , handling of properties related to cases , records of information and materials about individuals who were fined , and stolen and hijacked mobile vehicles , etc.
( hong kong , macao , and taiwan ) sun yun - suan dead of diseases in taipei
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 15. taipei news : sun yun - suan , who was the honorary chair of the board of the taiwan strait exchange foundation , died of acute myocardial infarction , acute cardiac failure complications , and septicemic shock , in the early morning of the 15th in taipei .
sun yun - suan was born november 11 , 1913 , in penglai , shandong , and graduated from the electrical engineering department of harbin industrial university .
he was a member of the tenth and thirteenth central committees of the kmt , a member of the eleventh and twelfth standing central committees , and a member of the fourteenth central evaluation committee , the chair of the presidium of the central evaluation committee , and a member of the fifteenth central evaluation committee .
he took positions including " transportation minister , " " economic minister , " and " premier of the executive yuan , " etc. of the taiwanese authorities .
heilongjiang develops assessment and strategy projects for water pollution impacts of songhua river on ecological environment
xinhua news agency , harbin , february 16 ( reporter : hu tao ) . to do a good job with the subsequent monitoring , pollution prevention and control work during the songhua river 's frozen and low water and ice - melting periods , heilongjiang province will actively implement assessment and strategy projects for the water pollution impact of songhua river on the ecological environment .
the reporter learned from the environmental protection bureau of heilongjiang province that the assessment and strategy projects for the impacts of the songhua river big pollution accident on the ecological environment organized and led by the state 's environmental protection bureau have determined 15 specialized subjects that are divided into five aspects , including emergent environmental assessment and strategy , ecological effect assessment and human health , pollution control projects , comprehensive assessment , and technological concentration , and they are scheduled and arranged to be completed in three phases .
currently , there are a total of 10 scientific research institutes and colleges and more than 60 individuals who have assumed technological research work on the 14 subjects .
as it is presented , environmental protection departments and related scientific research organizations will regard the five subjects as emergent environmental assessment and strategy ones , and make every effort to solve the environmental problems the masses are most concerned by ,
which include the concentration of featured pollutants in the main control section and predictions of the total escape amount ; assessment of the pollution impacts on the safety of aquatic products from the songhua river ; assessment of the impacts on the safety of randomly obtaining water along both banks of the river and the underground water supply ; a study on a plan of emergent purification technology for secure urban water supplies ; and a study on the regularity of pollutant residues and their melting away in the frozing and melting processes of the songhua river .
the environmental protection departments of heilongjiang province will also further strengthen environmental supervision and investigation along the banks of the songhua river , and strictly investigate and punish activities of illegally discharging pollutants and constructions that cause serious pollution .
heilongjiang will send environmental law enforcement workers to urge and guide locals to conduct small - river basin environmental control , and perfect the environmental control system for branches such as the ashi river , the hulan river , and the tangwang river , etc.
peking university sets up mourning hall to express condolences over academician wang xuan
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 15 ( reporter : li jiangtao ) . through several days of tense arrangements , the mourning hall for academician wang xuan that was set up at the memorial of the hundred - year anniversary of peking university was formally opened at 9 a.m. on the morning of the 15th . by noon of that day , several hundred people had come and offered their condolences .
before the mourning hall 's opening time , about 8 a.m. that morning , several dozen people had waited in a long line outside the hall 's gate .
inside the memorial hall , the reporter saw the dark , horizontal banner with the calligraphy " express profound condolences over academician wang xuan " hanging on the wall of the memorial of the hundred - year anniversary of peking university .
below the banner , there was a big picture of wang xuan that was more than ten square meters in size . wang was wearing a pair of glasses , smiling with a scholarly air .
several cypress trees and several dozen wreaths were put along both sides of the picture .
an elegiac couplet on a wreath was written like this : " it began in the qin dynasty , prospered in the tang dynasty , glorified china , and skillfully laid a foundation ; the contemporary bi sheng said farewell to the lead age , greeted the electronic one , and drew a blueprint . "
low - volume funeral music was mingled in the mourning hall , in a solemn and respectful atmosphere .
among groups who came to express their condolences , there were leaders , teachers , students of peking university , and friends , colleagues , students , neighbors of academician wang xuan , and also , many strangers who did not know him .
some of them held fresh flowers in their hands ; some carried flower baskets ; everybody , wearing small white flowers on their chests , slowly walked to the picture of academician wang xuan , and bowed to express their condolences .
many could not help but weep warm tears .
zhang wenbin , who was the director of the state 's cultural relic bureau and an old alumnus of peking university , told the reporter that , more than ten years ago , when he worked in henan province , he invited professor wang xuan to give a report on scientific and technological innovation for cadres of the provincial party committee .
" the conduct and academic studies of academician wang xuan are the model for us to learn . he made important contributions for the country and society , and people will never forget him . "
jin ruilin , a professor at peking university 's law school , has been an old friend and neighbor of wang xuan for more than 40 years .
he just left the hospital several days ago , and insisted on coming today to say farewell to his old friend .
when mr. jin wrote his words in the visitors ' book , he could not help but sadden and wipe the tears pouring from his eyes many times with tissues .
he told the reporter that professor wang xuan lived a very simple life , " when he lived in tongfu yuan , he had already been a professor and had accomplished significant achievements . but he still lived in a very small one - level house for many years .
he later moved to chengze yuan , where he had a space of 70 to 80 square meters , and lived there for more than ten years .
he refused an offer when peking university provided him a big 140 - square - meter flat in the academician building located in lan qiying ; he also refused an upper - floor flat provided by fangzheng building .
mr. jin recalled and said with deep emotion that when wang xuan visited foreign countries , he simply refused to take positions with very good offers provided by foreign institutions .
" he insisted on not applying for the title of academician at the beginning ; then he gave up and filled out an application only after mr. zhou peiyuan went to get him moving him many times . "
another thing that moved mr. jin was wang xuan 's attitude toward the training of young people , " he himself stressed many times that what should be found and relied on are not what achievements i have achieved , not myself , but the training of young people . "
mr. jin said that when wang xuan was around more than 50 years old , he started to pay attention to cultivating young people . he had stressed that we should pave a path , be willing to become a human ladder , and make way for young people .
" it is not easy at all for a very accomplished scientist to do this . "
the reporter learned from the peking university news center that the mourning hall for academician wang xuan will open to the public for people coming from various circles to express their condolences from 9 a.m. to 4:00 p.m. every day from 9 a.m. on february 15 to 12:00 noon on february 19 .
professor wang xuan of peking university died from a disease after the failure of a medical treatment at 11:03 p.m. on february 13 at beijing xiehe hospital . he was 70 years old . he was praised as a " contemporary bi sheng , " and had assumed positions including vice - chair of the national political consultation conference , academician of the chinese academy of sciences , academician of the chinese engineering academy , and academician of the third world 's academy of sciences .
( foreign affairs ) china 's national people 's congress establishes exchange mechanism with chilean parliament
wu bangguo attended the signature ceremony and signed the agreement
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 15 ( reporter : rong yan ) . president of the national people 's congress wu bangguo attended the signature ceremony for a political dialogue and relation agreement established between china 's national people 's congress and the chilean parliament , and signed the agreement document on the 15th .
the exchange mechanism between china 's national congress and the chilean parliament has been formally established .
as it has been learned , senate president of the chilean parliament romero and president of the chamber of deputies asensio had signed the agreement a few days ago in the chilean capital of santiago .
according to the agreement , both sides will follow the principles determined by the communique on the establishment of diplomatic relations between china and chile , establish a political dialogue relation between china 's national people 's congress and chile 's parliament , set up a dialogue committee , hold irregular meetings in turn in the two countries , and jointly promote thorough development of relations between the two countries .
ambassador of the chilean embassy in china cabrera and others attended the signature ceremony .
china to implement protection regulation on dissemination rights for information networks
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 15 ( reporters : zhou wei and li fei ) . many networks and websites currently rely on republishing a lot of news and reports from newspapers and magazines to increase their click rates , but many of them are neither authorized , nor pay related fees . to cope with this , director of the copyright department of the state copyright bureau wang ziqiang said in a press conference , held by the news office of the state council on the 15th , that the state council will explain about the implementation of the protection regulation on dissemination rights for information networks , on the issue of paying for republishing works on the internet .
wang ziqiang said that according to existing laws and regulations , regarding those works published in newspapers , as long as their authors did not state that " they cannot be used , " newspapers can use those works without their authors ' permission , but at the same time should pay them , and the state copyright bureau has made the payment standard specifically for newspaper reprint practices according to the law .
however , according to regulations in existing laws , newspapers have the right to such legal permissions , but the internet currently does not have rights for such legal permissions .
according to related interpretations made by the people 's supreme court , the legal permission for newspaper reprints is applied to the internet , i.e. to any small or short articles published in newspapers or on the internet , whose authors did not state that " they cannot be used , " the internet can use them without permission , but at the same time needs to pay their authors .
but because the legal interpretation does not determine the payment standard , the internet has not made payments when it used those works in practice .
" regarding whether the internet use of published small or short works applies to the legal permission , it still needs to be determined according to the laws . "
wang ziqiang said : " whether it will be included in a category of law depends on the confirmation of the implementation of the protection regulation on dissemination rights for information networks this year . "
( international ) russian military says georgian parliament 's resolution will not affect russia 's peacekeeping activities
xinhua news agency , moscow , february 15 ( reporter : song shiyi ) . xie duofu , a news officer for the russian defense ministry , told the media on the 15th that the resolution made by the georgian parliament on russia 's peacekeeping troops will not affect the russian military 's peacekeeping activities in the short term , and russian troops will continue to fulfill their peacekeeping mission in the conflict area of south ossetia .
the chair of the russian independent state affairs committee of the state duma ( lower house of the parliament ) , kokoshin , made a speech and indicated regarding the resolution made by the georgian parliament on russia 's peacekeeping troops , on the same day the resolution was published , that the resolution will harm the stability of the situation in that area and negatively impact the relations between russia and georgia .
he stressed that the resolution made by the georgian parliament is a further bad step toward damaging the relations between russia and georgia .
he thinks that the georgian accusation against the russian side is absurd .
the georgian parliament passed the resolution on that day , and requested russia 's peacekeeping troops to stop their peacekeeping activities in south ossetia , but did not set a concrete deadline for russia 's peacekeeping troops to withdraw .
the georgian parliament accuses russia 's peacekeeping personnel of a failure to fulfill their designated obligation , and regards the actions taken by russia in the conflict area as " trying to annex georgian territory . "
the georgian parliament requests the georgian government to take an active action and consider inviting international peacekeeping troops - to be stationed in the conflict area of south ossetia - to replace the peacekeeping activities currently undertaken by russia in that area .
the georgian parliament also requests the government to revise a related agreement that determined the stationing of russia 's peacekeeping personnel in the conflict area .
south ossetia is an autonomous georgian state , and borders with russia 's republic of north ossetia .
it announced its own independence after the soviet union collapsed , and has been confronting georgia 's central government for a long time .
russia currently has a peacekeeping battalion of 500 soldiers stationed in that area .
the troops stationed there are based on the agreement signed by four parties - including russia , georgia , north ossetia , and south ossetia - in 1992 .
large fire occurs at liaoyuan hospital ; four individuals responsible to be prosecuted as liable for big accident as suspects
xinhua news agency , changchun , february 16 ( reporter : zhou liquan ) . after the large fire disaster occurred at the central hospital of liaoyuan city in jilin province , an accident investigation group determined that 11 individuals are responsible , and among them , the head of the electrician team of the hospital , zhang diankun , and three other persons will be prosecuted as liable for the big accident .
the central hospital , the largest one in liaoyuan city , experienced a big fire on december 15 , 2005 , which eventually took 39 lives .
the total burned area in this fire disaster was more than 5,000 square meters .
as it has been learned , this is the biggest fire accident in the national medical and health system since new china was established .
as was investigated , at around 16:30 on the day the accident occurred , there was a sudden power failure at the central hospital of liaoyuan city . based on the hospital 's electrical circuit design , if there is a power failure , the circuit breaker in the transformer box should automatically switch to a backup socket to maintain normal power supply for the hospital . but at that time the circuit breaker did not automatically switch to the socket . zhang diankun , the head of the technician team , forced the power supply without investigating and clarifying the cause of the power failure , and caused the fire disaster .
those smoky underground cables , which should be laid out on a flat surface in very good order , were tangled together without any order , and fire prevention layers should be set up .
thus , three individuals including zhao yongchun , the 57 - year - old head of the electrical equipment installation team of the textile company of liaoyuan city , sun fenglin , a retired cadre ( senior engineer ) from the liaoyuan power affairs bureau , and jin taicheng , a reemployed retiree worker at the central hospital of liaoyuan city , will be prosecuted as suspects in the liability for the big accident .
first tourism ceremony in guizhou for china 's rural village tourism held in tianlong tunbao
xinhua news agency , guiyang , february 16 ( reporter : shi xinrong ) . on the morning of the 16th , adults and children were all wearing their festive costumes together and smiling cheerfully in tianlong village , tianlong towship , pingba county , guizhou province .
at 10:30 a.m. , after the five - grain sacrifice to the year activity had ended , zheng peiqin , an 80 - year - old villager wearing a long - sleeved , light green gown , first banged the gong for the first tourism ceremony of china 's rural village tourism in guizhou .
tianlong tunbao village is a typical representative of rural village tourism development in guizhou , and a display model of national rural village tourism .
the " tunbao people " have a history of more than 600 years as the descendents of those stationed troops who were sent there during the hongwu period of the ming dynasty .
locals wearing blue gowns with wide belts and sleeves can be found everywhere here . the ancient han culture and clothes are maintained very well in tunbao village .
as has been learned , based on the advantage of cultural tradition , tianlong village has been developing rural village cultural tourism since 2002 , and the ticket income for entrances alone was 3.8 million yuan in 2005 . more than 47 % of farmer households have participated in the tourist business through food and restaurant , transportation , sale of tourist merchandise , etc. farmers ' income per capita has increased from 1,300 yuan in 2002 to 2,640 yuan in 2005 .
as director of the tourism bureau of guizhou province yang shengming stated , after the first tourism ceremony in tianlong tunbao , 35 tourism projects will be developed for rural village tourism activities in guizhou under the theme of " new countryside , new tourism , new experience , and new trend . "
more than 130 villages have developed various rural village tourism projects in guizhou so far , and more than 600,000 farming households had been lifted from poverty through tourism development in the entire province by 2005 .
housing prices increased 5.5 % in 70 cities nationwide ; housing prices in shanghai continued to fall in january
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 16 ( reporter : liu zhen ) . in january of this year , housing prices increased 5.5 % in 70 large and medium cities nationwide compared with that of last year , and the rate of price increases fell 0.7 % compared with that of last month .
housing prices in shanghai continued to fall .
the data published by the state 's development and reform committee and the state 's statistics bureau on the 16th demonstrate that among 70 large and medium cities , most housing sales prices increased on the average by a small margin in january of this year compared with that of last year . the rate of housing price increases was more than 10 % in hohhot and dalian ; however , housing sale prices in shanghai continued to fall by a small margin , falling 0.4 % compared with last year .
the statistics in the same way demonstrate that the housing sales prices in shanghai increased 19.1 % in the first season of last year , compared with that of the year before last year . the trend changed after that . since the second half of last year , the price has demonstrated a downward trend by a small margin , compared with that of the year before last year .
in january of this year , the sale price of newly built commercial housing in 70 large and medium cities increased 6.9 % compared with that of last year , and the rate of price increases fell 0.2 % compared with that of last month .
cities that experienced higher rates of increase in sale prices for newly built commercial housing compared with that of last year include 18.9 % in dalian , 14.7 % in hohhot , 10.0 % in shenzhen , 9.1 % in chengdu , 8.4 % in beijing ; but the increased price rate in shanghai fell 3.1 % compared with that of last year .
central organization department of ccp requires further strengthening of supervision work for selection and appointment of leaders and cadres
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 16. the central organization department recently printed and issued a suggestion regarding strengthening the supervision work for cadres .
the suggestion requires that party organization departments at every level should strictly control , care for , and protect cadres , and conduct supervision work for cadres at every stage of cadres ' cultivation and education , review and test , selection and appointment , and routine management , and establish , perfect , and strengthen prevention work , promptly discover problems in the supervision work mechanism , seriously correct them , and truly strengthen the supervision work for selection and appointment of leaders and cadres .
the suggestion points out that the primary tasks of the organization departments for cadre supervision include , first , supervision of the leadership team and leaders , and its priority is to strengthen supervision of the major leader of a leadership team ; second , supervision of the selection and appointment work of leaders of the party and administrations , and its priority is to supervise and review implementation of the working regulation on selection and appointment of leaders of the party and administrations .
with regards to the supervision of the leadership team and leaders , the suggestion proposes that the ideal and good - faith education and anti - corruption and honesty promotion education should be consistently adhered to , and those educations should be practiced in cultivation , selection , control , and supervision of cadres , guide and urge leaders to strengthen their training of the party spirit , and stick to strengthening the ideological and ethical frontline , emphasizing that the party is established for the public , the administration is for the people , and anti - corruption is to prevent degeneration .
honesty and self - discipline should clearly come up as requirements when talking with newly promoted cadres in their appointment meetings .
leadership teams at every level should be urged to stick to the democratic centralization system , establish and perfect rules and procedures for meetings and decision - making , and carefully practice the system that integrates collective leadership with individual responsibility in related fields .
the supervision over the major leader of a leadership team should be emphasized . leaders of organization ( personnel ) departments should frequently talk with and conduct heart - to - heart talks with the major leader of a leadership team at the next lower level to learn the status of his ideology , work , and style of work , etc.
a routine control and supervision system should be established and perfected for leaders ; the status of ideology and style of work of a leadership team should be regularly learned and analyzed , and suggestions and measures should be come up with to solve problems .
a warning talk and letter inquiry system for leaders should be practiced . once the hint of a problem emerges , a warning talk or letter inquiry should be promptly conducted .
as for those obvious problems with leaders reported by the masses , they should be carefully investigated and clarified ; if a problem is true , the leader concerned should be criticized and educated , or disciplined by appropriate organizational measures ; if any leader violates any regulation or law , he or she should be transferred to the law or discipline enforcement organization to be investigated ; if a leader is found innocent through an investigation , a clarification should be addressed for him or her in a proper manner .
at the same time , strengthening supervision of cadres should be integrated by encouraging cadres to boldly explore and develop innovations , and excellent cadres should be discovered and promptly commended .
the suggestion requires that organization ( personnel ) departments at every level should truly strengthen the supervision work of selection and appointment of leaders of the party and administrations .
supervision measures on the stages of cadres ' recommendation , nomination , test and review , discussion , and determination , etc. , should be further perfected , and cadres should be strictly selected and used , and vigorous support should be provided for recommendation and selection of cadres who are politically reliable , talented at their work , maintain a good style of work , and are trusted by the masses of people to take leadership positions at every level .
the implementation status of the regulations for cadre appointment should be reviewed vigorously . any conduct that violates the regulations for cadre appointment should be seriously investigated and disciplined , and indecent practices and corruption in the use of cadres should be firmly contained .
a supervision and investigation system for any serious violation of regulations for the use of cadres should be practiced to further strengthen supervision , investigation , and disciplinary work .
a system of selection and appointment of cadres - and investigation of their working responsibility - should be established and perfected . based on the principle that power matches responsibility , every stage of the cadres ' selection and appointment work , including the main body of responsibility and content of responsibility , should be scientifically defined , and an investigation method should be clarified to strengthen investigation work .
the supervision role played by the masses should be fully exercised to establish and perfect a reporting mechanism that is " convenient , secure , and highly efficient . "
the supervision role played by public opinion should be fully employed , and the status of cadres ' selection and appointment work should be notified to the news media within an appropriate amount of time , and accept the supervision of public opinion .
the suggestion proposes that a coordination mechanism of cadre supervision work should be further perfected .
organization ( personnel ) departments should strengthen coordination with discipline investigation organizations , establish a work communication system , contact person system , and responsibility system , with discipline investigation organizations in the aspect of cadres ' fair administration and their party spirit , in order to strengthen integrated supervision .
visiting and investigation work should be carefully and well done with discipline investigation organizations ; visiting and investigating methods can be improved and perfected to promote visiting and investigation quality .
an auditing system for leaders ' economic responsibility should be carefully practiced with auditing organizations .
an internal supervision mechanism for cadres ' selection and appointment work of the organization departments should be perfected .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) taiwan authorities heavily fine leading high - tech enterprise for violation of regulation and investment on mainland .
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 16 ( reporter : chen jianxing ) . on the 15th , an economic affairs administration of the taiwan authorities decided to fine lianhua electronics corporation ( shortened name : " liandian " ) , one of " the two giant wafer producers " in taiwan , 5 million new taiwan dollars , because it " violates regulation by providing assistance and participating in creation " for hejian science and technology company on the mainland .
taiwan 's china times reported that this is the first case used by taiwanese authorities to fine and discipline a taiwanese business that invested on the mainland since chen shui - bian came up with the economic and trade policy of " actively controlling and effectively opening . "
as has been reported , a person from the taiwan " report and review committee of the economic department " said that the reason why liandian was fined was because it violated " the regulation of the people 's relation across the strait , " and regulations of " permission methods for investment and technological cooperation on the mainland . "
in the future , the report and review committee will fine tsao hsing - cheng , former chair of the board of liandian , according to the circumstances .
the " liandian case " originated in february 2005 , and by then taiwanese investigation departments had used around a hundred people to hurriedly search the residences and offices of several high - level liandian employees , and alleged that liandian was suspected of investing on the mainland and " illegally providing capital , technology , and human resources " to hejian science and technology company .
tsao hsing - cheng , the then - chair of the liandian board , later publicly stated that liandian did not violate any of the taiwan authorities ' regulations , and the assistance liandian provided to hejian science and technology was for liandian 's long - term interest , and liandian would lose business opportunities if it did not enter the mainland market as soon as possible .
after that , the " financial supervision and control committee " of the taiwan authorities fined liandian 3 million new taiwan dollars for its violation of the regulation regarding disclosure of commercial information .
on january 9 , 2006 , the liandian board accepted tsao hsing - cheng 's resignation , and he was formally prosecuted for violation of regulations on investment on the mainland within several hours .
liandian and taiwan semiconductor manufacturing company ( shortened name : tsmc ) are called " the two giant wafer producers " in taiwan , and both are leading high - tech enterprises on the island .
a series of investigations and disciplinary actions taken by the taiwan authorities against liandian have attracted close attention from various circles on the island .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) second " macao in my heart " essay competition soliciting essays from overseas chinese worldwide
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 17 ( reporter : li kun ) . the organization committee for the second " macao in my heart " essay competition announced in beijing on the 17th that it is soliciting and collecting essays titled " macao in my heart " from overseas chinese worldwide .
the essay competition is jointly sponsored by the macao foundation and baihua wenyi press 's " overseas essay edition , " and vice - chair of the china writers ' association chen jiangong and others are directors of the evaluation committee .
the first " macao in my heart " essay competition was launched in 2004 , on the five - year anniversary of macao returning to the motherland , and received active responses from literature lovers at home and abroad . the organization committee received a total of more than 8,000 essays for the competition , and more than ten winners at home and abroad were invited to macao special region to accept awards .
wu zhiliang , an administrative member of the macao foundation , announced in a press conference on the 17th that " macao 's historical urban area " was listed on the world heritage list last year , which not only means that the long - term way of life and community management mode of macao 's people have been acknowledged by the world , but also that the humane tradition of " peace with differences " and inclusiveness and friendship of the chinese nation has been inherited and developed in macao special region ; and thus , the government of macao special region has designated 2006 as macao 's " year of world cultural heritage . "
wu zhiliang said that it is in the good cultural atmosphere that the macao foundation and baihua wenyi press ' " overseas essay edition " decided to collaborate again and sponsor the second " macao in my heart " essay competition , and hopes that participants demonstrate their patriotic and loving macao sentiment , the elegant and unique humane atmosphere of macao , and the new peaceful and prosperous sceneries of the special region , and further establish macao 's outstanding image as a cultural city .
as has been announced , the due date for essays is september 1 of this year for this competition , and " overseas essays edition " will create a special column to publish selected essays .
